body_text.text:
Between November 2013 and April 2014, 188 episodes of ARI from 163 patients were reported to the research team (49 men and 114 women), with a mean age of 83 years (SD = 9.2; range: 59–101) for men and 85 years (SD = 7.2; range: 62–101) for women (Table 2
). These patients were from 14 institutions, as four institutions did not report any episode (Table 3
).
